BMW Says First-Quarter Sales Rose, Sees Record Sales in 2011

-- B y   M a r i a j o s e   V e r a
-- 
2011-04-08T09:00:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-08/bmw-says-first-quarter-sales-rose-sees-record-sales-in-2011.html
Bayerische Motoren Werke AG (BMW) 
deliveries rose 21 percent in March to 382,758 vehicles in the
first quarter, the company said in an e-mailed statement. BMW-
brand sales gained 21 percent, the company said.  “We expect to increase sales to a new record of
significantly more than 1.5 million vehicles,” sales chief  Ian Robertson  said in the statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mariajose Vera in Munich at 
 mvera1@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Angela Cullen at   acullen8@bloomberg.net . 